      "turn_index": 0
    },
    {
      "text": "\"There was a young man.\"\n",
      "tags": [],
      "outcome": "Continue",
      "variable_changes": {},
      "visit_changes": {},
      "turn_index": 1
    },
    {
      "text": "Harris is not letting me off any more.\n",
      "tags": [],
      "outcome": "Continue",
      "variable_changes": {},
      "visit_changes": {},
      "turn_index": 1
    },
    {
      "text": "\"You seriously entertained that possibility?\"\n",
      "tags": [],
      "outcome": {
        "Choices": {
          "presented": [
            {
              "text": "Yes",
              "index": 0,
              "tags": []
            },
            {
              "text": "No",
              "index": 1,
              "tags": []
            },
            {
              "text": "Lie",
              "index": 2,
              "tags": []
            }
          ],
          "selected": 1
        }
      },
      "variable_changes": {},
      "visit_changes": {},
      "turn_index": 1
    },
    {
      "text": "\"No. Not for more than a moment.\" He seemed to know all about me.\"\n",
      "tags": [],
      "outcome": "Continue",
      "variable_changes": {},
      "visit_changes": {},
      "turn_index": 2
    },
    {
      "text": "The way Harris is staring I expect him to strike me.\n",
      "tags": [],
      "outcome": {
        "Choices": {
          "presented": [
            {
              "text": "Yes",
              "index": 0,
              "tags": []
            },
            {
              "text": "No",
              "index": 1,
              "tags": []
            }
          ],
          "selected": 1
        }
      },
      "variable_changes": {},
      "visit_changes": {},
      "turn_index": 2
    },
    {
      "text": "\"It wasn't,\" I reply.\n",
      "tags": [],
      "outcome": "Continue",
      "variable_changes": {},
      "visit_changes": {},
      "turn_index": 3
    },
    {
      "text": "He simply nods.\n",
      "tags": [],
      "outcome": "Continue",
      "variable_changes": {},
      "visit_changes": {},
      "turn_index": 3
    },
    {
      "text": "\"Go on with your confession.\"\n",
      "tags": [],
      "outcome": "Continue",
      "variable_changes": {},
      "visit_changes": {},
      "turn_index": 3
    },
    {
      "text": "That gives me pause.\n",
      "tags": [],
      "outcome": "Continue",
      "variable_changes": {},
      "visit_changes": {},
      "turn_index": 3
    },
    {
      "text": "\"This young man was blackmailing you over your affair?\"\n",
      "tags": [],
      "outcome": "Continue",
      "variable_changes": {},
      "visit_changes": {},
      "turn_index": 3
    },
    {
      "text": "Whatever it was they put in my drink is wearing off.\n",
      "tags": [],
      "outcome": {
        "Choices": {
          "presented": [
            {
              "text": "Yes",
              "index": 0,
              "tags": []
            },
            {
              "text": "No",
              "index": 1,
              "tags": []
            },
            {
              "text": "Tell the truth",
              "index": 2,
              "tags": []
            },
            {
              "text": "Lie",
              "index": 3,
              "tags": []
            }
          ],
          "selected": 2
        }
      },
      "variable_changes": {
        "drugged": false
      },
      "visit_changes": {},
      "turn_index": 3
    },
    {
      "text": "\n",
      "tags": [],
      "outcome": "Continue",
      "variable_changes": {},
      "visit_changes": {},
      "turn_index": 4
    },
    {
      "text": "\"Yes. I suppose he was their agent.\"\n",
      "tags": [],
      "outcome": "Ended",
      "variable_changes": {},
      "visit_changes": {},
      "turn_index": 4
